column5: Hi all,I have begun experimenting with casting for pike and musky, never really gave it much of a go but am learning to like it a lot this year, there are some really nice pike on the reefs and in the weeds this time of year and the muskies seem to be in 2' to 5' in the weed also, here are a couple of musky I got on film a couple days ago.VIDEOhttps://youtu.be/EKGUFBul7XY
Be careful, LA, you might catch the fever! John
Question! Why did I see your bilge pump running a number of times in your videos?
Great videos, love the tail-walking! Keep posting!
